================================================================
Models
================================================================

Pessoa does NOT bundle or redistribute model weights. By default it
loads the following models on demand via Ollama. Use of those models
is governed by their respective licenses, not by Pessoa's Apache-2.0
license:

    gemma4:e2b
        Google Gemma family.
        Use of Gemma models is subject to Google's Gemma Terms of Use:
        https://ai.google.dev/gemma/terms

    nomic-embed-text
        Nomic AI, Apache-2.0
        https://huggingface.co/nomic-ai/nomic-embed-text-v1.5

Changing MODEL or EMBED_MODEL in src/chat.py will subject your
deployment to the license terms of whatever weights you point those
at. Verify compatibility before commercial use.

